{"tid":868685,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【血淚工程】過期救生衣害死港珠澳大橋工人 海事處知情不告","createTime":"2018-10-19T16:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T11:54:43.000Z","uid":89543,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"22f8ad6122855e9c5960ee2510d8f2bfe46e091e","tid":868685,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:28:58.000Z","msg":"下周二開通的港珠澳大橋的香港段工程共奪去十名工人性命，《蘋果》揭發當中有工人疑因救生衣失靈枉死！工人吳清睞2014年於港珠澳工程駁船搬重物時失平衡墮海，他原已穿上了可保命的自動充氣救生衣，但他跌落水後救生衣卻未能自動充氣，吳最終溺斃。海事處調查雖揭發救生衣確有故障、更未有按規定每年至少檢查保養一次，但海事處仍涉嫌放生承建商不作檢控。死者父母對真相感到憤怒，要求解釋不檢控的原因，還愛兒一個公道。"},{"pid":"8427bc96e529945ec69a7c5b8f9acc4c4d5a3ce9","tid":868685,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:29:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181019/58813564?fbclid=IwAR2OQlzjnEW9kQoVtrHEIlXfnqbX2Fcb4Up6RrUnB5G0J0rUHNEM_aIQ8Sk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181019%2F58813564%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2OQlzjnEW9kQoVtrHEIlXfnqbX2Fcb4Up6RrUnB5G0J0rUHNEM_aIQ8Sk&d=k1mwhY0xzbygSZy31giZGAHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=7ff67b29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181019%2F58813564%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2OQlzjnEW9kQoVtrHEIlXfnqbX2Fcb4Up6RrUnB5G0J0rUHNEM_aIQ8Sk&h=0ae23ad8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181019/58813564?fbclid=IwAR2OQlzjnEW9kQoVtrHEIlXfnqbX2Fcb4Up6RrUnB5G0J0rUHNEM_aIQ8Sk</a>"},{"pid":"90f61595b70cc39fcc9888acb375fdb332002ce8","tid":868685,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a25f0ebb4887c3866a249fa9a5ef9c3f2d86fc","tid":868685,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:46:45.000Z","msg":"1997-2010"},{"pid":"f7e644738ad960a6e6e946ca656d0d90e